'''华为Mate X2'''是[[华为|华为]]生产的一款基于{{link-en|Android}}系统的[[奢侈品|高端]][[可摺疊式智能手機|可摺疊式智能手機]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Huawei launches new foldable phone as U.S. sanctions continue to hurt smartphone business|url=https://www.cnbc.com/2021/02/22/huawei-mate-x2-launch-specs-price-release-date.html|accessdate=2021-02-22|author=Kharpal|date=2021-02-22|first=Arjun|work=CNBC|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210302224459/https://www.cnbc.com/2021/02/22/huawei-mate-x2-launch-specs-price-release-date.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，折叠形态为横向内折。該手機是[[華為Mate_X|華為Mate X]]和Mate Xs的后续产品。这款手机于2021年2月22日亮相<ref>{{Cite web|title=Huawei’s Mate X2 foldable adopts Samsung’s dual-screen design|url=https://www.theverge.com/2021/2/22/22294983/huawei-mate-x2-fold-specs-price|accessdate=2021-02-22|author=Porter|date=2021-02-22|first=Jon|work=The Verge|language=en|archive-date=2021-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417230503/https://www.theverge.com/2021/2/22/22294983/huawei-mate-x2-fold-specs-price|dead-url=no}}</ref>。華為Mate X2共有四种颜色，分别是黑色、白色、浅蓝色和玫瑰金<ref name = "gsm" />。

